{"word":"Bread","slug":"bread","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bread</b> Called the Staff of Life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=4&verse=16'>Eze 4:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=5&verse=16'>Eze 5:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=14&verse=13'>Eze 14:13</a><br/> Kinds of:<br/> - Bread of affliction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=27'>1Ki 22:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=127&verse=2'>Psa 127:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=9&verse=4'>Hos 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=20'>Isa 30:20</a> <br/> - Leavened<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=13'>Lev 7:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=17'>Lev 23:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=7&verse=4'>Hos 7:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=4&verse=5'>Amo 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=33'>Mat 13:33</a> <br/> - Unleavened<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=3'>Gen 19:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=2'>Exo 29:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=19'>Jdg 6:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=28&verse=24'>1Sa 28:24</a> <br/> Made of:<br/> - Wheat flour<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=2'>Exo 29:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=22'>1Ki 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=11'>1Ki 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=16'>Psa 81:16</a> <br/> - Manna<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=8'>Num 11:8</a> <br/> - Meal<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=12'>1Ki 17:12</a> <br/> - Barley<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=13'>Jdg 7:13</a> <br/> How prepared:<br/> - How prepared:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=2'>Exo 29:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=23'>Exo 29:23</a> <br/> - Mixed with honey<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=31'>Exo 16:31</a> <br/> - Mixed with leaven, or ferment<br/> <a href='S:Leaven'>Leaven</a> <br/> - Kneaded<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=18&verse=6'>Gen 18:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=8&verse=3'>Exo 8:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=34'>Exo 12:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=28&verse=24'>1Sa 28:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=8'>2Sa 13:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=18'>Jer 7:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=7&verse=4'>Hos 7:4</a> <br/> - Made into:<br/> b Loaves<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=10&verse=3'>1Sa 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=17'>1Sa 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=18'>1Sa 25:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=14&verse=3'>1Ki 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=8&verse=14'>Mar 8:14</a><br/> b Cakes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=19'>2Sa 6:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=12'>1Ki 17:12</a><br/> b Wafers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=21'>Exo 16:21</a