ibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=21'>Jer 37:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=37'>Mar 6:37</a><br/> Sacrificed<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=6'>Lev 21:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=8'>Lev 21:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=17'>Lev 21:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=22'>Lev 21:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=25'>Lev 22:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=36'>1Sa 2:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=9'>2Ki 23:9</a> <br/> - By idolaters<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=18'>Jer 7:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=44&verse=19'>Jer 44:19</a><br/><a href='S:Shewbread'>Shewbread</a>; <a href='S:Offerings'>Offerings</a> <br/> Figurative<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=55&verse=2'>Isa 55:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=17'>1Co 10:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=9&verse=10'>2Co 9:10</a> <br/> - Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=35'>Joh 6:35</a> <br/> Symbolic of the body of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=26'>Mat 26:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=7'>Act 20:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=11&verse=24'>1Co 11:24</a>"}]}